snippet.title: Jazz Jackrabbit
snippet.description: Jazz Jackrabbit was a popular 2D platform game developed by Epic Megagames in 1994. In this game you had to control Jazz, a green rabbit that looks like a cross between Rambo and Bugs Bunny.
